    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Bureau-cabinets typical of fine furniture originating in the 17th century that feature cabinets of drawers or pigeon holes, fronted by one or more doors, and supported on a stand from which it may be detached.</Note_Text>
